  "prompt": "How many offices does Google have around the world?  Which countries are they in?",
  "response": "Google, a subsidiary of Alphabet Inc., has a vast global presence with offices in numerous countries around the world. While the exact number of offices can fluctuate due to expansions, closures, or consolidations, Google has a presence in over **70 countries** as of recent updates. These offices range from large campuses (like Googleplex in Mountain View, California) to smaller regional offices.\n\n### Notable Countries with Google Offices:\nHere\u2019s a list of some of the major countries where Google has offices (this is not exhaustive but highlights key regions):\n\n#### **Americas:**\n- United States (Mountain View, New York, San Francisco, Seattle, etc.)\n- Canada (Toronto, Montreal, Waterloo)\n- Brazil (S\u00e3o Paulo, Belo Horizonte)\n- Mexico (Mexico City)\n- Argentina (Buenos Aires)\n\n#### **Europe:**\n- United Kingdom (London)\n- Ireland (Dublin)\n- Germany (Munich, Berlin, Hamburg)\n- France (Paris)\n- Switzerland (Zurich)\n- Netherlands (Amsterdam)\n- Sweden (Stockholm)\n- Spain (Madrid)\n- Italy (Milan)\n- Poland (Warsaw)\n\n#### **Asia-Pacific:**\n- India (Hyderabad, Bengaluru, Gurgaon)\n- China (Beijing, Shanghai)\n- Japan (Tokyo)\n- South Korea (Seoul)\n- Singapore (Singapore)\n- Australia (Sydney, Melbourne)\n- New Zealand (Auckland)\n\n#### **Middle East & Africa:**\n- Israel (Tel Aviv)\n- United Arab Emirates (Dubai)\n- South Africa (Johannesburg)\n\n### Types of Offices:\nGoogle\u2019s offices serve various purposes, including:\n- **Engineering and R&D centers** (e.g., Mountain View, Zurich, Bengaluru)\n- **Sales and marketing offices**\n- **Data centers** (e.g., Finland, Iowa, Taiwan)\n- **Startup incubators** (e.g., Google for Startups campuses)\n\n### How to Find the Latest Information:\nFor the most up-to-date and comprehensive list of Google offices, you can visit Google\u2019s official **\"Google Offices\"** page or their **Careers site**, which often lists locations where they are hiring. Additionally, Google Maps can be a helpful tool to locate Google offices around the world.\n\nLet me know if you'd like more specific details about any region!",
